o Built on NumPy, SciPy, matplotlib. 
o Provides model evaluation metrics and pipelines. 
• Use Cases: Predictive modeling, data preprocessing, feature 
engineering. 
• Pros: Beginner-friendly, easy-to-use API, great for classical ML. 
